<li id="cite_note-gassintro-3"><b><a href="#cite_ref-gassintro_3-0" title="">^</a></b> William H. Gass, Introduction to <i>The Anatomy of Melancholy</i>, New York Review of Books 2001 <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0940322668" class="internal">ISBN 0-940322-66-8</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-4"><b><a href="#cite_ref-4" title="">^</a></b> Thomas Mallon, <i>The New York Times Book Review</i>, October 3, 1991</li>
<li id="cite_note-5"><b><a href="#cite_ref-5" title="">^</a></b> Nick Lezard, "<a href="http://books.guardian.co.uk/print/0,3858,4065172-99931,00.html" class="external text" title="http://books.guardian.co.uk/print/0,3858,4065172-99931,00.html" rel="nofollow">Classics of the Future,</a>" <i>The Guardian</i>, September 16, 2000.</li>
</ol>
</div>
