<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Anatomy_of_Melancholy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Further reading">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="news" id="CITEREF.5B.5BWilliam_Monahan.5D.5D"><a href="/wiki/William_Monahan" title="William Monahan">William Monahan</a> (Fall 2001). <a href="http://bookforum.com/archive/fall_01/monahan.html" class="external text" title="http://bookforum.com/archive/fall_01/monahan.html" rel="nofollow">"Remedial Reading: William Monahan on The Anatomy of Melancholy, by Robert Burton, introduction by William H. Gass"</a>. <a href="/wiki/Bookforum" title="Bookforum">Bookforum</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://bookforum.com/archive/fall_01/monahan.html" class="external free" title="http://bookforum.com/archive/fall_01/monahan.html" rel="nofollow">http://bookforum.com/archive/fall_01/monahan.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-04-14</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Remedial+Reading%3A+William+Monahan+on+The+Anatomy+of+Melancholy%2C+by+Robert+Burton%2C+introduction+by+William+H.+Gass&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BWilliam+Monahan%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BWilliam+Monahan%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=Fall+2001&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BBookforum%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fbookforum.com%2Farchive%2Ffall_01%2Fmonahan.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:The_Anatomy_of_Melancholy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> The introduction by author <a href="/wiki/William_H._Gass" title="William H. Gass">William H. Gass</a> runs just under 10 pages.</li>
